(70, 4, '2012-06-20 18:54:07', 'Magento Community Edition 1.7.0.1 now available! ', 'We have just released an updated version of Magento Community Edition, version 1.7.0.1. This update delivers new, minor functionality and fixes for some potential security vulnerabilities.', 'http://www.magentocommerce.com/blog/comments/magento-community-edition-1701-released/', 0, 0),
