(181, 3, 'ps-04|Enabled|Runner 2||Runner2 is the sequel to the critically acclaimed and IGF award winning BIT.TRIP RUNNER.In the style of the BIT.TRIP series, Runner2 is a rhythm-music platforming game.&nbsp; Players will run through fantastic environments, using brand new moves, to brand new soundtracks as they run, jump, slide, kick, and soar toward the goal of tracking down the Timbletot and thwarting his evil plans to destroy not only our world, but every world there is.5 exciting worlds120 tantalizing levels and 5 death defying BOSS battles!Play as 8 different characters - find secret areas to unlock new and zany costumes!|Runner2 is the sequel to the critically acclaimed and IGF award winning BIT.TRIP RUNNER.Genre: Family GameRelease Date:10/10/2012|321|1', 1163),
(181, 1, 'ps-04|Enabled|Runner 2||Runner2 is the sequel to the critically acclaimed and IGF award winning BIT.TRIP RUNNER.In the style of the BIT.TRIP series, Runner2 is a rhythm-music platforming game.&nbsp; Players will run through fantastic environments, using brand new moves, to brand new soundtracks as they run, jump, slide, kick, and soar toward the goal of tracking down the Timbletot and thwarting his evil plans to destroy not only our world, but every world there is.5 exciting worlds120 tantalizing levels and 5 death defying BOSS battles!Play as 8 different characters - find secret areas to unlock new and zany costumes!|Runner2 is the sequel to the critically acclaimed and IGF award winning BIT.TRIP RUNNER.Genre: Family GameRelease Date:10/10/2012|321|1', 1162),
(180, 1, 'ps-03|Enabled|101 Puppy Pets||Over 101 Puppies to Adopt and Love! Choose from over 101 cute, adorable puppies&mdash;or simply adopt them all! You''ll never be bored with so many new best friends to groom, pamper, play with and love! Enjoy a game of fetch in the park! Teach your puppy to sit, speak, dance &amp; more. Reward your puppy with a treat after each trick! Enter your puppy into dog shows &amp; earn money to buy fun upgrades, including toys, food, furniture &amp; more! Buy cute clothes &amp; dress up your puppies in 3D! Zoom in, zoom out, tilt &amp; rotate in real 3D. Watch your puppy, up close &amp; personal!Immersive 3D Virtual World: Enjoy full 3D environments! Go to the park, romp in the yard &amp; moreMultiple Puppy Breeds: Choose from Labrador Retrievers, Siberian Huskies, Dalmatians, Beagles, Golden Retrievers, Jack Russell Terriers &amp; more!Over 101 Puppy Toys &amp; Upgrades: Unlock new items as you care for your petPersonalized Fur Tint: Ever want a pink Dalmatian? Now’s your chance!Visible Puppy StatusPlay Multiple Saved Games10+ Pet ProfilesDog Show CompetitionsReal Fur Textures|Over 101 Puppies to Adopt and Love! Choose from over 101 cute, adorable puppies Genre: Family GameRelease Date:10/10/2012|353|1', 1204),
(180, 3, 'ps-03|Enabled|101 Puppy Pets||Over 101 Puppies to Adopt and Love! Choose from over 101 cute, adorable puppies&mdash;or simply adopt them all! You''ll never be bored with so many new best friends to groom, pamper, play with and love! Enjoy a game of fetch in the park! Teach your puppy to sit, speak, dance &amp; more. Reward your puppy with a treat after each trick! Enter your puppy into dog shows &amp; earn money to buy fun upgrades, including toys, food, furniture &amp; more! Buy cute clothes &amp; dress up your puppies in 3D! Zoom in, zoom out, tilt &amp; rotate in real 3D. Watch your puppy, up close &amp; personal!Immersive 3D Virtual World: Enjoy full 3D environments! Go to the park, romp in the yard &amp; moreMultiple Puppy Breeds: Choose from Labrador Retrievers, Siberian Huskies, Dalmatians, Beagles, Golden Retrievers, Jack Russell Terriers &amp; more!Over 101 Puppy Toys &amp; Upgrades: Unlock new items as you care for your petPersonalized Fur Tint: Ever want a pink Dalmatian? Now’s your chance!Visible Puppy StatusPlay Multiple Saved Games10+ Pet ProfilesDog Show CompetitionsReal Fur Textures|Over 101 Puppies to Adopt and Love! Choose from over 101 cute, adorable puppies Genre: Family GameRelease Date:10/10/2012|353|1', 1205),
(178, 1, 'ps-01|Enabled|Sonic and the All-Stars||Sonic and the All-Stars cast line up on the starting grid once again to battle for supremacy in the ultimate race.&nbsp; Compete across land, water and air in incredible transforming vehicles that change from cars to boats to planes mid-race.&nbsp; Master your driving skills as you drift, barrel role and boost to overtake your rivals, or use your weapons tactically and unleash your All-Star move to gain the winning advantage. It’s not just your fellow racers you need to watch out for, as the road falls away beneath you, or the river runs dry, new routes emerge and your vehicle transforms to take advantage of the terrain. Discover alternative routes and short cuts as you perfect the course in this adrenaline fuelled dash to the finish line - racing will never be the same again.This is not just racing, it’s racing transformed!Fully Transformable Vehicles - This is no ordinary race. Each character is equipped with their own unique vehicle that can transform into a car, boat and plane to take advantage of the changing terrains. Each vehicle handles differently and players must master all three to triumph.&nbsp; Choose your Racer - Race as over 20 legendary All-Stars. The starting line-up has been transformed as new iconic characters from the world of SEGA join the race. What other game sees a hedgehog battle it out against a monkey, a sky pirate and an axe wielding dwarf!Dynamic Tracks - Take to land, sea &amp; air as you race through 16 dynamically changing courses inspired by SEGA’s illustrious gaming history. Discover alternate routes, find new power-ups and avoid emerging hazards as you race to victory &ndash; every track feels different.Tools of Devastation&nbsp; - Utilise an arsenal of devastating weapons which require skill to aim, shoot, evade and block. The All-Star Moves also return, this time the more daring and stylishly you race, the more your All-Star meter increases allowing you to unleash carnage on your o